{"TopicId":215273,"ForumId":197,"TopicTitle":"Planting Flag on Space Craft","CreatedByName":"B3RT0","CreatedById":227927,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-17T06:12:40Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"B3RT0","CreatedById":227927,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-17T06:12:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003EKSP Version - v0.1.1.0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003EOperating System and version -\u00A0 Windows 10\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003ECPU and GPU models - AMD \u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003ERyzen 5 5600X, RTX 3080\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDescription of the bug -\u00A0 Landed on Laythe, had 4 kerbals stand on top of craft. Made one Kerbal plant a Flag. After flag is planted space craft sinks into ground, slides, flag floats in air. If kerbals jump on to ground they freeze in place.\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EFixes / Workarounds (if known..) do not plant flag on craft\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EA list of ALL mods. - No mods\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOther Notes / Screenshots / Log Files (if possible..)\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-22T21:26:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224260860\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022215273\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221679033560\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022227927\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022B3RT0\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 3/17/2023 at 7:12 PM, B3RT0 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDescription of the bug -\u00A0 Landed on Laythe, had 4 kerbals stand on top of craft. Made one Kerbal plant a Flag. After flag is planted space craft sinks into ground, slides, flag floats in air. If kerbals jump on to ground they freeze in place.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022zG4k4HJ.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/zG4k4HJ.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHaha. Maybe it works for one Kerbal and not multiple ones?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIssues:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nThe flags are attached to the ground,\u00A0not the craft so you move the craft the flags remain in the same place they were placed above the terrain.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nDoesn\u0027t work in space. The Kerbal can do the animation, but nothing ends up being placed.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nOne time the Kerbal stopped being able to move was after loading a quicksave.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCome on Intercept Games. These flags need to stay attached to the rocket! haha \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pandaman","CreatedById":130621,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-22T21:52:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDidn\u0027t \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/205123-nate-simpson/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022205123\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/205123-nate-simpson/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Nate Simpson\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0say something about us finding imaginative ways to find bugs.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:joy:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/joy.png\u0022 title=\u0022:joy:\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-22T23:09:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224264132\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022215273\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221679521928\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022130621\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022pandaman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, pandaman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDidn\u0027t \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/205123-nate-simpson/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022205123\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/205123-nate-simpson/\u0